    <item>
      <title>英国保守党领袖竞争对手就税收和移民问题展开辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/rivals-pitch-leadership-plans-for-ousted-tories-key-takeaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四位接替里希·苏纳克成为英国保守党领袖的候选人将出席在伯明翰举行的保守党年度会议，向党员们介绍自己的竞选策略，党员们将在一个月后做出最终决定。在两位领跑者凯米·巴德诺赫和罗伯特·詹里克最近遭遇挫折后，保守党议员和官员告诉彭博社，竞选结果更加公开透明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/rivals-pitch-leadership-plans-for-ousted-tories-key-takeaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朔尔茨再次呼吁尽快结束南方共同市场谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/scholz-makes-fresh-plea-for-speedy-conclusion-to-mercosur-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨再次呼吁迅速完成欧盟与南美四个经济体之间一项主要贸易协定的谈判，该协定遭到法国的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/scholz-makes-fresh-plea-for-speedy-conclusion-to-mercosur-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:19:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国计划在 2025 年削减 600 亿欧元支出并提高税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 寻求收回不断扩大的预算赤字并增强投资者对法国的信心，该国计划明年削减约 600 亿欧元（664 亿美元）的支出并提高税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿塞拜疆领导人流亡批评者在法国遭受袭击后死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/exiled-critic-of-azerbaijani-leader-dies-after-attack-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位直言不讳的阿塞拜疆总统伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫的批评者在法国遭遇袭击后死亡，他在袭击中被三名身份不明的袭击者刺了好几刀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/exiled-critic-of-azerbaijani-leader-dies-after-attack-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
